abstract: --In England the  Winter comes hard upon the professional tramp. abstract: The question arises,  What are pearls? Are they a morbid concretion of matter produced in the endeavor to heal a wound or to cover some irritating body that cannot easily be ejected from the shells? abstract: LONDON, March 12. The Mark Lane Express, in its review of the British Corn trade for the past week says: "Spring sowing has been carried on vigorously during the week, and, the land being in excellent condition, a large breadth of Spring Corn has been sown. The Autumn-sown Wheat-plant preserves its healthy appearance. Pastures promise an early and abundant Hay crop. English Wheat has been marketed in small quantities and unsatisfactory condition.
